{"tid":1459102,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"<<下一束光 >> - 送給處身崩壞時代的香港人","createTime":"2019-08-12T16:07:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T16:07:34.000Z","uid":92107,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"5d5be865caeb294632890b910f1f749a7b6e8059","tid":1459102,"uid":92107,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T16:07:34.000Z","msg":"過去兩個月<br />\n香港的汗血淚<br />\n差不多流光了<br />\n即使處身於黑暗<br />\n我們仍然要相信<br />\n前進還有風光<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/p/B1EQNeAgpeN/?igshid=1vt7cr6l7wxh4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FB1EQNeAgpeN%2F%3Figshid%3D1vt7cr6l7wxh4&d=9IUie9AXCQLlCDjKIEsB2xfhc2i76iEVsdTpjF8%2BTp8%3D&h=4b41e80d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FB1EQNeAgpeN%2F%3Figshid%3D1vt7cr6l7wxh4&h=582057cf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/p/B1EQNeAgpeN/?igshid=1vt7cr6l7wxh4</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄歌詞:<br />\n前進於那方還有風還有光<br />\n出生於廢墟曾怯慌如煉鋼<br />\n無奈尋覓過承受過期限都過就似經過死亡<br />\n前進可有光從這方能夠窺看<br />\n即使訊息渺茫仍舊發放<br />\n重覆退敗過重新再發現海港"}]}